<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Bei ding ei tai lei chim-um,
 Khuo hung vak ding ei tai;
 Zie ni chuh ngaiin ka tau,
 Zing khuo hungvak ding chu;
 Zan hun chuh thim mahlele, Nilopi anai tai;
 Lopi takin leng hitiu; Imanuel gamah.

[V2]
 2. Aw, Krista tuikhuk na hi,
 Hehpihna tuikhuk chuh;
 Ka tep tai zie lei ahin,
 Van ah tamzaw dawn ka;
 Ziechun tuipi lien tak chu, A zahngaih na'n a dim;
 Lopi takin leng tang ka, Imanuel gam ah.

[V3]
 3. Mo in moneipa thuom sang,
 In a mel a et bang;
 Lopina chuh enlo in,
 Ka Lalpa mel en ka;
 Chan ding Lallukhuk sangin, A khut liemna en ka;
 Lopina pen Belam No, Imanuel gamah.

[V4]
 4. Lungsieta ei enkawl in,
 Ka phat ei vawp saka;
 Lungkham na tungsek mahleh,
 A hehpihna'n ei nem;
 Chawian ka ei Puipa chuh, Bang cheng ei Guotsakpa;
 Lopina mun ka tun tieng, Imanuel gam ah.</lyrics>
<title>THE SANDS OF TIME</title>
<hymn_number>362</hymn_number>
</song>